  "id": "RAW_7b4df992",
  "title": "不只是出图工具，Lovart 正在让设计告别返工",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==&mid=2247499287&idx=1&sn=864e707d49abaf74a758ee3d08d0cb61",
  "date": "2025-12-23 02:00:00",
  "author": " 有新Newin",
  "siteName": "有新Newin",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" style=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015633\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"237\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"100015635\" data-ratio=\"0.4216691068814056\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1366\" style=\"width:100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0becaf9d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5ka3eYG2e3EuMbjTc9DDh1xria27XwbficH17R7JcgGDrZFeTbzCBjdRyLg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\">\n    <br></span></p>\n  <p class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-remoteid=\"\" data-asynid=\"\" src=\"\" data-src=\"\" align=\"\" alt=\"\" border=\"\" data-ratio=\"\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"\" aria-label=\"\" aria-braillelabel=\"\" aria-description=\"\" height=\"\" hspace=\"\" ismap opacity=\"\" sizes=\"\" title=\"\" type=\"block\" usemap=\"\" vspace=\"\" width=\"\" data-width=\"\" data-height=\"\" data-croporisrc=\"\" data-cropx1=\"\" data-cropx2=\"\" data-cropy1=\"\" data-cropy2=\"\" data-cropselx1=\"\" data-cropselx2=\"\" data-cropsely1=\"\" data-cropsely2=\"\" data-backw=\"\" data-backh=\"\" data-copyright=\"\" data-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-gallerysupplier=\"\" data-cardimg=\"\" data-fileid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100015464\" data-positionback=\"\" data-imgqrcoded=\"\" data-imgid=\"\" data-upload=\"\" data-fromlib=\"\" data-aiimageid=\"\" data-cacheurl=\"\" data-retry=\"\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-aiimagesource=\"\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"有新Newin\" data-alias=\"NewinData\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/wqO5B9doEHfWpviblkX0cCTHkGRJYxSBgwSqgeKicI9Qm9jOia9oQ19BsiblkJBYDAsu0moqoJrZ8xCC5oWyDjoViaQ/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"探索新科技，聚焦新价值。\" data-id=\"Mzg3NDkyMTQ5Mw==\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这一年里，设计工具的更新速度明显快过了设计需求本身。模型越来越多、参数越来越强，但真正落到项目中，问题反而变得更具体了：不是“能不能生成”，而是“能不能把一整件设计任务顺利做完”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">Lovart 的产品形态也正显现出差异，并没有把重点放在“帮用户选模型”上，而是直接承接设计任务本身。通过一句 prompt，生成的不再是零散素材，而是已经按照实际使用场景组织好的结果，从节日 KV、活动海报到多尺寸社媒图，整体结构和延展关系一开始就被考虑进去。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这种体验上的变化，并不来自某一个模型参数，而来自对设计流程的整体理解。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">设计思维、接近真实设计师的任务拆解与完成能力，加上始终可编辑的画布，共同构成了一条完整的设计工作流</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在 NanoBanana Pro 的加持下，Lovart 也成为目前使用这一模型最顺滑、最成熟的产品形态之一。短时间内积累的 1000 万 + 专业用户，以及 8000 万美元的 ARR，意味着这种“直接把设计做完”的方式，已经跨过尝鲜阶段，开始进入稳定使用的区间。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">最累的，往往不是想点子</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">尤其是在当前圣诞、跨年以及新年这样高度商业化、节奏又密集的节点里，品牌真正需要的，从来不只是几张好看的图，而是一整套能快速落地、风格统一、还能反复调整的视觉方案。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这类项目中设计师真正被消耗的，往往不是创意阶段，而是创意之后的那一长串执行工作。一套设计从来不只是一张主视觉，还要不断被延展成海报、社媒图、不同尺寸的物料。哪怕方向已经确定，后面依然会被复制、裁切、重排这些细碎动作拖慢节奏。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">即使 AI 已经参与进来，这种状态也并没有发生根本变化。生成变快了，但生成之后的事情依旧被拆散：适配在这里，修改在那边，文件在不同工具之间来回流转。节日节点一密集，这种被拆开的工作方式就会被放大，时间和注意力被消耗在反复对齐上。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">把同样的需求交给 Lovart 时，设计推进的方式开始不一样了。输入的不再是“先做一张看看”，而是一个完整的节日设计目标，生成的也不再是零散的几张图，而是一整套已经按照使用场景组织好的结果。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">主视觉、海报、多尺寸社媒图在同一个画布里同时出现，结构关系一开始就被理顺。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"714\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1512\" data-imgfileid=\"100015626\" data-ratio=\"1.2705882352941176\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1190\" data-width=\"1190\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cb5fe265&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5kafkuyvNiaXGlk6PkoHNpXuic3DlzKNAk4scicyWMHdoiaKs9qYdlTvv6v3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">从画面本身来看，这套方案并没有靠堆叠元素制造节日感，而是通过统一的视觉语言完成整体表达。温暖而克制的氛围、金色与暖红为主的配色、大量留白保留品牌调性，每一张图都明显属于同一个体系。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015627\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5563839701770736\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2146\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2146\" data-height=\"1194\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"313\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eea674c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5kaqNfkTH22MMiaqPNBClx9Mbh7KKPULAiaMlC3vAdgYKib6NnJZUJR1UjDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">更重要的是，这种“成套生成”让使用方式变得清晰。哪一张是主视觉，哪一张用于竖版传播，哪一张适合社交平台，不需要再事后补想象。修改、微调和延展，都发生在同一套结果之上，而不是反复从头开始。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">这种成套输出带来的变化，在实际项目里非常直观。每一张图该怎么用、会出现在哪里，不需要再事后补想象。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">不管是圣诞、跨年还是新年，不同主题下沿用的是同一套设计骨架，修改和调整都发生在同一个结果之上。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">当节日从圣诞过渡到跨年或新年，设计真正面临的挑战，并不是重新想主题，而是在不打断原有结构的前提下完成切换。视觉需要变化，但使用场景、传播节奏和物料结构，最好保持稳定。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015623\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9661016949152542\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1180\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1180\" data-height=\"1140\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"543\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b02a2cbc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5kafzw91ldUccpeFr9jkRJ59WACqGQnHKuvNB7HU8icJbxic5Q6EjONSnTg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">在这组跨年 / 新年方案中，Lovart 延续了圣诞项目中已经建立好的设计框架，只对主题元素和氛围进行调整。结构没有被推翻，主视觉、海报和多尺寸社媒图依然在同一逻辑下展开，设计从一个节日自然走向下一个，而不是反复回到起点。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015620\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5528301886792453\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2120\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2120\" data-height=\"1172\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"311\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=581122e0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5kaa0LDI8YNnboGp4bJc3Sor4D5lcCFVEeRGqkgWA3RSaZAL8VAqUcSZg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">也正是在这种连续的推进中，设计的角色发生了变化。生成不再是必须立刻定型的终点，而是一个可以继续往前走的起点。</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">设计从一开始就以“整套结果”为目标，也为后面的调整、细化和延展提供了更多空间。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015619\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.36632747456059206\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2162\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"2162\" data-height=\"792\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"206\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ae19b3c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FwqO5B9doEHcBB5WiaIpDP0s3B1N9OT5kahFOia1qQ2q5jXlUVajOAAtU0hMxOtiaKaFoP5xVbUYQzN5Zdunds6qXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">生成完成后，整套设计会保留在同一个画布中，直接就能继续操作。放大、移除背景、Mockup、编辑元素或文字，都在上方工具栏里随手完成，修改发生在原结果之上，不需要重新开始。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">▍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:17px;\">返工不再是设计流程的一部分</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"caret-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:15px;font-family:Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span textstyle=\"\">项目被真正推进起来后，很多变化其实发生得很安静。不是效率突然暴涨，也不是某个功能让人惊呼，而是一些原本会下意识回避的修改，开始变得没那么犹豫了。文案要不要先定、细节要不要留到最后，这些过去需要反复权衡的决定，慢慢不再成为负担。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-al